data.title: Yesterday Stephen Bray invited me to a special screening of The Color Purple. It was especially emotional since four years ago on Christmas...
data.meta_description: 73 likes, 7 comments - zimmermanstan on December 24, 2023: "Yesterday Stephen Bray invited me to a special screening of The Color Purple. It was especially emotional since four years ago on Christmas Eve, we lost my good friend Allee Willis. She was part of the extraordinary team, along with Stephen and Brenda Russell, who wrote the music & lyrics to the theatre production. Processing so many feelings as this huge achievement opens tomorrow. Congrats to all!".
